{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea2e1561f4","title":"戚本禹给聂元梓蒯大富的电话记录","origin":"1967年3月北京玻璃总厂红卫兵联络站编《中央首长讲话（2）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"74b0f8603c","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":13,"articleId":"ea2e1561f4"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"57434e107b","name":"戚本禹","type":"人物"},{"id":"8e7eaace26","name":"聂元梓","type":"人物"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9014e20fdf","name":"戚本禹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7354d92f84","type":"title","text":"戚本禹给聂元梓蒯大富的电话记录","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"},{"id":"fb768ec657","type":"authors","text":"戚本禹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"},{"id":"dd06c2a545","type":"appellation","text":"聂、蒯同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"},{"id":"1d97c21f94","type":"paragraph","text":"关于北京造反公社情况我不了解，他们的代表们曾找过我，因为抽不出时间，一直未能见到。我曾表示过，希望北京革命组织，在毛泽东思想基础上搞大联合，不要搞小团体主义。所传我们对造反公社的批评，如果指的这个意思，是有的。但是，这不是批评，而是一种愿望。另外，大联合组织，是否用“北京公社”的名义，希望你们商量一下。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"},{"id":"60e08a6335","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们在毛泽东思想基础上联合起来。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"},{"id":"6f2e84895b","type":"paragraph","text":" 戚本禹一九六七年二月十三日","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4"}],"page":{"id":"f1a4503d81","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"ea2e1561f4","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}